extendedInfo.description: Contains nursery rhymes that are most popular with children all over the world! Each rhyme has an illustration. Your child will love it!IncludesBaa Baa Black SheepCobbler, Cobbler, Mend My ShoeHumpty DumptyHickory, Dickory DuckEency Weency SpiderJack and JillLittle Miss MuffetMary Had a Little LambOne Two Buckle My ShoePussy Cat, Pussy CatRainTwinkle, Twinkle, Little Starand many more!!!
